  "title": "7506 - Electrician | Eunos",
  "description": "<p>Working Days: Monday – Saturday<br />Working Hours: 8.30am – 5.30pm<br />Salary: $ 3,000 – $ 3,600<br />Working Location: Eunos <br />(Will need travel to customer site)<br /><br />Industry: Interior Design & Construction Company<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Overall planning, coordination and supervision of electrical work.</li><li>Replace damaged wires, electrical components and protective devices; install wiring, distribution boxes, switches, sockets, lighting, etc.</li><li>Lay out wiring and install equipment according to drawings and single-line diagrams.</li><li>Use testing instruments to test voltage, current, insulation, etc.</li><li>Ensure all installation and maintenance work complies with safety standards and electrical codes.</li><li>Submit work reports and technical records as required by the company.</li><li>Quickly analyze sudden electrical faults and provide solutions.</li><li>Collaborate with engineers, technical supervisors and contractors to complete project tasks.<br /> </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Several years of work experience, including experience as an electrician in the construction industry.</li><li>Familiar with construction techniques, building materials and relevant laws and regulations.</li><li>Possess Singapore Class 3 License is an advantage.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
